舒緩啲?<br />\n感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4bb3459a6fcc7a54aa3c37b17d677f414b21d93","tid":1160151,"uid":217942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T16:16:29.000Z","msg":"努責現象<br />\n<br />\n呼吸問題"},{"pid":"c904547aa4031ab8911bc32e1504806ee8bf0bf8","tid":1160151,"uid":64376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4bb3459a6fcc7a54aa3c37b17d677f414b21d93","tid":1160151,"uid":217942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T16:16:29.000Z","msg":"努責現象<br />\n<br />\n呼吸問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T16:20:43.000Z","msg":"請問可以點樣避免/改善?<br />\n做多啲帶氧練好心肺功能有無幫助?"},{"pid":"97fe2279c0812b3dd66761f9774331ba3465ff01","tid":1160151,"uid":815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c904547aa4031ab8911bc32e1504806ee8bf0bf8","tid":1160151,"uid":64376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4bb3459a6fcc7a54aa3c37b17d677f414b21d93","tid":1160151,"uid":217942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T16:16:29.000Z","msg":"努責現象<br />\n<br />\n呼吸問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T16:20:43.000Z","msg":"請問可以點樣避免/改善?<br />\n做多啲帶氧練好心肺功能有無幫助?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T15:50:23.000Z","msg":"唔好格硬做咁重<br />\n飲多啲水 同埋唔夠訓就唔好操腳"}]}